<br>
And if i'm trying to put together a raid on Phin this weekend, about how many people would i need to get together? Thanks much. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwraithwavefeaamael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wraithwave FeaAmael</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://keith.vaughan.home.mindspring.com/img/ball3.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/30/01 10:43:20 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Guildless wizards...</span><hr size=1> I'm not going to lie.  These quests (ALL of them) are designed around highly &quot;uber&quot; mobs and zones.  Unless you have an EXCELLENT network of friends who are strong enough and organized enough to get the job done, it will be very difficult.  Let me break the pieces down...<br>
<br>
Phinigel - Can do with 1 upper 50's group.  That is probably the &quot;easiest&quot; one for a guildless wizard to get.  &quot;Easiest&quot; shouldn't be misunderstood.  The rarity of the drop and the fact that it is highly contested will make it tough.  But we're just talking about the ability to take down the mob.<br>
<br>
Venril Sathir - You're best shot is to try to get in on a guild raid.  Since the staff drops so frequently, many of the guilded wizards will have theirs already.  Therefore, by default, you'll have a shot.<br>
<br>
Broken Golem - I would say this one will be most difficult if not in a guild.  It is already a VERY contested spawn, at least on my server.  The difficulty doesn't lie in the toughness of the mob.  The difficulty lies in the fact that you have to clear a major portion of fear in order to do it.  People won't simply drop everything and go to fear for that reason alone.  They would only go when there is something in it for them.  And here is the kicker... many major guilds with level 60(or near) members don't WANT to go to fear anymore.  It is a major hassle to them.  Hell, I'm IN a guild and it is still pulling teeth.<br>
<br>
<br>
Is getting the epic impossible without being in a guild?  No, far from impossible.  However, it will be a long process which will test your patience beyond belief.  It is hard enough for those of us IN a guild.  Imagine the difference already being behind the eight ball.<br>
<br>
This wasn't meant to be discouraging.  Just realistic.  BUT, by no means should you seek out a guild JUST for the reason of finishing your epic.  That would be shallow.  I care about PEOPLE in my guild.  Not loot.  I'm sure they wouldn't appreciate it very much if I only was along for the loot.<br>
<br>
Good luck. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showMessage?topicID=1357.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showMessage?topicID=1352.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=1356.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.threadControl?topicID=1356.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1356.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1356.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum<option value="gra